  "title": "MASSEUR (NON-MEDICAL)",
  "description": "<p>Roles &amp; Responsibilities</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Skilful and ethical in treating patients with therapeutic massage, cupping and scrapping</li>\n  <li>To establish strong rapport with the doctors/physicians, and seek ways for potential cooperation in raising standards of TCM services</li>\n  <li>Perform other duties and responsibilities that may be assigned from time to time</li>\n  <li>Cleaning and sanitizing work areas, changing treatment room sheets, and sterilizing all instruments and equipment before each use.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Effective communication skills.</li>\n  <li>Proven experience working as a massage therapist.</li>\n  <li>Able to work on weekends / public holidays</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>",
